doctype html
head
  meta(charset='UTF-8')
  meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge')
  meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
  title Risk1
  link(rel='stylesheet' href='../static/Style.css')
  script(src='../static/JavaScript.js' defer='')
body 
  br
  h1    Please assess the risk level of the event described below 
  br
  p#RiskDescription
    | You have received a message stating that you are eligible for a special loan of up to NIS 100,000, but in order to receive it, you are required to click on an unfamiliar link. The message was received from a sender named "must," and it contains a link with random letters and numbers in the address. Another link, similar to the first one, is attached to the message, which claims to allow the removal of the message.
  form(action='/insertClick' method='POST')
    input(type='hidden' name='redirect_url' value='/Risk2-Group2')
    input(type='hidden' name='RiskID' value='Risk1-Group2')
    .slidecontainer
    label#riski(for='Riskrate') 0 - No Risk
    input#myRange(type='range' name='Riskrate' class='riskSlider' min='0' max='100' step='1' oninput="document.getElementById('sliderValue').innerHTML = this.value; enableSubmit()")
    label#riski(for='myRange') 100 - Very High Risk
    p#sliderValue 50
    button(type='submit' id='submitRisk' disabled) Submit
